---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy">
  <section style="padding: 5rem 2rem; background: white; min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);">
    <div style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 900; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0 0 3rem;">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">We collect personal information you provide when creating an account or making a purchase, including name, email address, and payment information. We also collect usage data to improve our services.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">We use your information to process orders, provide customer support, send transactional emails, and improve our platform. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">3. Cookies</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">We use essential cookies to keep you logged in and maintain your cart. Optional analytics cookies help us understand how visitors use our site. You can disable optional cookies at any time.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">We employ industry-standard security including SSL encryption and secure token storage to protect your personal data.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting <a href="mailto:support@wowosim.com" style="color: #03def3;">support@wowosim.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
